      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "These are the steps I believe should be taken to close this:\r\n- [x] **Remove `Edit Label` in `Transaction View`**\r\n  - PR [#211](https://github.com/bitcoin-core/gui/pull/211) removed the ability to `Edit Label` in the `Transaction View`. The removal of this feature will prevent confusion that you are editing a unique identifier for that transaction. \r\n- [ ] **Add ability to add a `comment` to a Transaction** (this would be local on the machine)",
